00:02:59.230 --> 00:03:02.610
It is mapping the value
4 to two values.

00:03:02.610 --> 00:03:04.190
That is not allowed
for a function.

00:03:04.190 --> 00:03:09.470
A function has to map from a
value to only one other value.

00:03:09.470 --> 00:03:13.890
So the points on the graph
below do not represent a

00:03:13.890 --> 00:03:17.090
function, so I'll
just write a no.

